header.p: Transcription of The Instruction of Ptahhotep, in the version of Papyrus Prisse, following Zába (1956). The missing line numbers 6.1, 8.13, and 17.5 were inserted on the basis of Jéquier (1911). On p. 49, line number 12.4 was corrected to 13.4.
In lines 7.5 and 12.9, what seems to be M30 in Zába's transcription is here transcribed as M32.

bibliography.li: G. Jéquier. Le Papyrus Prisse et ses Variantes. Librarie Paul Geuthner, Paris, 1911.
Z. Zába. Les Maximes de Ptahhotep. Editions de L'Académie Tchécoslovaque des Science, Prague, 1956.
